Excuse me?

260
00:18:33,946 --> 00:18:35,280
I need your urine.

261
00:18:36,323 --> 00:18:38,283
You've got to be kidding.

262
00:18:38,951 --> 00:18:42,162
I don't know jack about cocaine.

263
00:18:42,746 --> 00:18:45,082
Like hell I'm giving you my urine!

264
00:18:47,626 --> 00:18:49,002
Is that right?

265
00:18:49,545 --> 00:18:53,173
I take it that you refuse
to cooperate with the investigation?

266
00:18:53,757 --> 00:18:56,593
I'm not letting out
even a single drop of urine!

267
00:18:57,678 --> 00:19:00,013
I'll ask you just one more time.

268
00:19:01,849 --> 00:19:06,436
You refuse to offer your urine
for testing, correct?

269
00:19:18,782 --> 00:19:20,993
So the NCD got the spoils,

270
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:24,329
and you returned empty-handed, did you?

271
00:19:25,122 --> 00:19:26,540
I apologize.

272
00:19:30,919 --> 00:19:32,254
Katsuragi.

273
00:19:33,672 --> 00:19:36,842
I hate beating around the bush,
so let me be direct with you.

274
00:19:37,342 --> 00:19:38,594
Yes, sir.

275
00:19:39,636 --> 00:19:41,555
The reason you're still here

276
00:19:41,638 --> 00:19:45,684
is that your father
is a senior commissioner and my superior.

277
00:19:47,352 --> 00:19:50,314
But I'm still aiming
to go higher, you see.

278
00:19:51,148 --> 00:19:54,026
Your accomplishments will serve
as my accomplishments.

279
00:19:54,109 --> 00:19:55,068
I'm aware.

280
00:19:55,152 --> 00:19:57,946
Then bring me results, not words.

281
00:19:59,072 --> 00:20:00,449
Never lose to the NCD again.

282
00:20:00,532 --> 00:20:01,575
Yes, sir.

283
00:20:04,286 --> 00:20:07,998
Kaga will maintain silence
in response to the NCD's questioning.

284
00:20:08,582 --> 00:20:13,462
As a drug addict, he should know
that he's dead if he leaks his suppliers.

285
00:20:16,006 --> 00:20:18,091
In the meantime go find his supplier.

286
00:20:18,884 --> 00:20:19,843
Yes, sir.

287
00:20:21,178 --> 00:20:22,262
Katsuragi.

288
00:20:23,013 --> 00:20:24,848
Use any means necessary.

289
00:20:25,515 --> 00:20:29,519
Utilize whatever is useful
and discard anything that isn't.

290
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:32,648
You're not just a police detective.

291
00:20:33,690 --> 00:20:35,525
You're a detective of the MPD,

292
00:20:36,193 --> 00:20:38,195
the foremost police organization.

293
00:20:40,948 --> 00:20:41,949
Yes, sir.

294
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:34,668
What are you doing?

295
00:21:34,751 --> 00:21:35,711
Unhand me!

296
00:21:36,378 --> 00:21:37,671
Let me go!

297
00:21:37,754 --> 00:21:40,549
Stop struggling! Stay still!

298
00:21:44,052 --> 00:21:45,429
Don't…

299
00:21:45,512 --> 00:21:48,932
You refused to cooperate
with the urine test, did you not?

300
00:21:49,016 --> 00:21:51,351
So I went and got a warrant for it.

301
00:21:53,645 --> 00:21:56,982
If a suspect refuses
to willingly provide their urine,

302
00:21:57,065 --> 00:22:02,070
we can get a court-issued warrant
to draw urine directly from the bladder.

303
00:22:02,154 --> 00:22:05,615
Directly from the bladder?
You can't mean--

304
00:22:07,159 --> 00:22:08,577
What the hell is that?

305
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:12,581
A catheter will now be inserted
into your genitals to extract urine.

306
00:22:13,123 --> 00:22:15,542
It will hurt like hell, but stay quiet.

307
00:22:16,126 --> 00:22:19,129
Wait! You've got to be kidding me!

308
00:22:20,547 --> 00:22:23,633
-Stop it!
-I'm dead serious.

309
00:22:24,634 --> 00:22:27,179
Let me go!

310
00:22:27,262 --> 00:22:29,556
It will hurt more if you keep moving!

311
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:32,476
No!

312
00:22:32,559 --> 00:22:33,852
-Go ahead.
-Okay.

313
00:22:34,561 --> 00:22:36,021
Stay still, okay?

314
00:22:36,104 --> 00:22:38,148
You'll injure your urethra!

315
00:22:38,231 --> 00:22:39,316
Stop!

316
00:22:39,399 --> 00:22:40,984
Stop it!

317
00:22:41,568 --> 00:22:42,986
No!

318
00:22:45,906 --> 00:22:48,450
Doctor, can you turn it this way?

319
00:23:03,090 --> 00:23:04,216
What do you want?

320
00:23:10,764 --> 00:23:12,724
Wait, what?

321
00:23:14,267 --> 00:23:15,352
What?

322
00:23:26,404 --> 00:23:29,991
<i>This adds damage to property</i>
<i>on top of inflicting bodily injury.</i>

323
00:23:30,575 --> 00:23:31,952
Are you mad?

324
00:23:32,035 --> 00:23:35,622
The NCD has Kurosaki, who'll use
any means to make a suspect talk.

325
00:23:36,123 --> 00:23:38,917
<i>His mother</i>
<i>wasn't just a regular meth addict.</i>

326
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:42,921
<i>She was fed meth</i>
<i>and forced into becoming a sex addict.</i>

327
00:23:43,004 --> 00:23:47,384
I said you would hurt those dear to you
and lose everything if you did drugs.

328
00:23:47,467 --> 00:23:50,345
Please, just come back
to your senses, you idiot!

329
00:23:51,429 --> 00:23:54,766
WILL KUROSAKI AND UMEZAWA
BE ABLE TO SAVE HER?

330
00:23:54,850 --> 00:24:00,772
ANY RESEMBLANCE TO ACTUAL PERSONS,
GROUPS, OR CASES IS PURELY COINCIDENTAL

331
00:24:00,856 --> 00:24:01,815
Subtitle translation by: Saim Ul Hassan
